**Bio | Ric P | Ricnology**

**| Innovation and Cybersecurity Governance Consultant |**

MBA-qualified professional with 10+ years of leadership in regulated industries, specialising in risk, compliance, and large-scale transformation. 

Experienced in directing operations and engaging boards, regulators, and government stakeholders.

Worked on projects across emerging technologies including AI, robotics, blockchain, and biotech (CRISPR, multiomic sequencing), supporting projects in governance, risk assessment, project delivery, and
financial management.

Now focusing on cybersecurity governance and cloud security resilience. Developing expertise in information security frameworks and technical fluency through hands-on training and labs.

Certifications include ISO/IEC 27001:2022 Lead Implementer, with CIPP and CISM in progress.

